y completing a project on your own or with other students with the guidance of a faculty advisor service learning project fund return to the trip location to test out a new idea or further build your expertise and network with financial support from the pmp current destinations view service learning trips in a larger map trip coverage study trips add perspective for mba students water service learning trip blog south africa service learning trip blog service board apprenticeship summer internships service learning student clubs service day service learning trips 2011 2012 california china kenya south africa thailand and cambodia united arab emirates oman past trips guatemala india new orleans in their words you are missing some flash content that should appear here perhaps your browser cannot display it or maybe it did not initialize correctly image stanford gsb service learning trip download and share program information admissions faculty & research alumni recruiters & companies giving executive education news about the gsb copyright 2009 stanford graduate school of business site help terms of use & policies stanford university
